  collectively broken — every item points at the same URL, has an empty body, and carries
  a placeholder title. This is the shape the soft quality gate must flag (URL_COLLAPSE,
  IDENTITY_COLLAPSE, BODY_EMPTY, TITLE_FALLBACK) without dropping anything.
  Each item has a valid pubDate + absolute link so it survives normalization.
-->
